        "rule is an object with optional fireRatingPattern, hostTypePattern,",
        "minOdMm, maxOdMm, plus a ulSystem field carrying the certified UL",
        "or EN 1366-3 system reference. Stamped on PEN_CERTIFICATION_TXT at",
